---
title: Truffled Onion Grilled Cheeses with Potato Wedges and Lemony Mixed Greens
description: Who said grilled cheese can’t be luxurious? This week, our chefs added a few twists to make the nostalgic dish extra-indulgent. We’re talking slices of fresh mozzarella, truffle-flecked caramelized onions, AND truffled sour cream for dipping. On the side, there’s roasted potato wedges and a heap of lemony mixed greens. Yeah, this is one grilled cheese you may just feel inclined to break out the white tablecloth for.
